<br>
Ry'Gorr is close if not better in AC to cleric quest armor.  <br>
Royal Frosted Velium Armor you can hang at the zone and loot what people don't need.  AC is better then EM from PoH.<br>
Cleric Quest Armor of course.  Easiest armor to obtain I think if you can't afford or are to low to hunt Ry'Gorr.<br>
Seb Scale BP is good AC and like 6 wis.  Better then Quest Armor.<br>
Guantlets of the Black.  Better then EM PoH Guants and good wisdom.<br>
Jasarith Armor in Karnor's is pretty decent but is No Drop so you need to hang at zone and hope to get some.<br>
<br>
I think your primary goal at lower levels is getting your Wisdom as close to 200 as you can.  You might have to sacrifice some AC to do this however depending on your race.  Once you start surpassing the 200 wis and get better Wisdom gear from planes ect, then you can start adding resist and/or Mana items. <p><img border="1" src="http://www.yellowspine.com/images/char1.bmp" width="360" height="94"></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilismeleetalk.showMessage?topicID=492.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilismeleetalk.showMessage?topicID=491.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilismeleetalk.threadControl?topicID=493.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilismeleetalk.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=493.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilismeleetalk.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=493.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub13.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="brellserilisfrm48">Town Crier (Rules & Announcements)<option value="brellserilisbrellserilisdiscussion">The Commons (General EQ Discussion)<option value="brellserilisfrm56">Salutations & Congratulations <option value="brellserilisfrm33">Dreams & Diversions (Off Topic)<option value="brellserilis